videos.description: Ish Smith makes a nice bounce pass to Jon Leuer who drives to the hoop and throws down a dunk with Giannis Antetonkounmpo in his face.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Smith feeds Leuer for nice slam) 2016/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smith feeds Leuer for nice slam

videos.description: Ish Smith makes his way into the paint and finishes in traffic with a nice layup while getting fouled.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Smith drives to basket for nice layup) 2016/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smith drives to basket for nice layup

videos.description: Marcus Morris lobs a pass to Andre Drummond who exhibits great athleticism by sinking a no-look, alley-oop layup off the backboard.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Drummond makes incredible no-look, alley-oop layup) 2016/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Drummond makes incredible no-look, alley-oop layup

videos.description: Ish Smith picks up a loose ball and finds Kentavious Caldwell-Pope in transition for a hard, two-handed slam dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Caldwell-Pope slams home dynamite dunk) 2016/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caldwell-Pope slams home dynamite dunk

videos.description: Tobias Harris gets the pass in transition and throws down a one-handed dunk just one second before the end of the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Harris hammers home one-handed dunk before buzzer) 2016/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harris hammers home one-handed dunk before buzzer

videos.description: Andre Drummond races into the paint to clean up Tobias Harris' missed layup and slam home a putback dunk over John Henson.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Drummond throws down putback dunk over Henson) 2016/10/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Drummond throws down putback dunk over Henson
